    "headline": "Gold Stocks Are in a Bear Market. The Case for Buying.",
    "summary": "Gold stocks are way down, and anyone seeking a bargain should at least give them a look.  The VanEck Gold Miners exchange-traded fund—home to some of the largest miners, such as  Newmont  and  Barrick Mining  —has slid 24% from its record high hit in late February.  The stocks are so-called leveraged plays on the commodity—when the price of the commodity falls, the stocks fall harder.",
